The current behavior suggests that `GetPatterns()` is returning a view of the internal list that updates when new patterns are added. This is not the behavior we want for immutability.

To fix this, we need to modify the `Verb` class to return a new list each time `GetPatterns()` is called, rather than returning a reference to the internal list.

